  "prompt": "Is MBA Guru, Kohat enclave, Delhi, a good coaching institute for CAT preparation?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, I don't have specific reviews or ratings for MBA Guru in Kohat Enclave, Delhi. However, when evaluating a coaching institute for CAT preparation, consider the following factors:\n\n1. **Faculty Quality**: Experienced and knowledgeable instructors can make a significant difference in your preparation.\n2. **Study Material**: Comprehensive and well-structured study materials are crucial for effective learning.\n3. **Mock Tests**: Regular practice through mock tests and an analysis of performance can help you gauge your preparation level.\n4. **Success Rate**: Look for the institute's track record in terms of the number of students who have successfully cleared the CAT and secured admissions in top B-schools.\n5. **Student Feedback**: Reviews and testimonials from past students can provide valuable insights into the institute\u2019s teaching methods and support.\n6. **Personal Fit**: Consider factors like batch size, location, timings, and your comfort level with the institute.\n\nIt\u2019s always a good idea to visit the institute, speak to the faculty, and talk to current or past students before making a decision. If MBA Guru meets most of these criteria positively, it could be a good option for your CAT preparation.",
